OL,3,CStormont to 'work out implications for
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland' of benefits shake-up
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's devolved government
OL,7,Fis set to work out the implications
OL,8,Ffor the region of a major shake-up of
OL,9,Fthe benefits system.
OL,11,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill has
OL,12,Fsaid she has concerns over the
OL,13,Fmeasures which include legislating to
OL,14,Ftighten the eligibility for the
OL,15,Fpersonal independence payment (Pip)
OL,16,Fand plans to raise it with London.
OL,18,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons said
OL,19,Fhe also has concerns but emphasised
OL,20,FStormont does not have the resources
OL,21,Fto mitigate the changes.
