OL,3,CStormont to 'work out implications for
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland' of benefits shake-up
OL,6,FStormont currently runs a number of
OL,7,Fmitigations against some previous
OL,8,Fbenefit system changes such as the
OL,9,Fbedroom tax and benefit cap.
OL,11,FSpeaking to media at Parliament
OL,12,FBuildings on Tuesday, Mr Lyons said
OL,13,Fmitigations for the new changes could
OL,14,Fcost #150 million.
OL,16,F"We will take time to analyse this,
OL,17,Fbut we do have to keep in mind as
OL,18,Fwell, we're talking about significant
OL,19,Fsums of money," he said.
