OL,3,CStormont to 'work out implications for
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland' of benefits shake-up
OL,6,F"If these are savings of around #5
OL,7,Fbillion for the UK as a whole, on
OL,8,Fpopulation basis alone, we're talking
OL,9,Fover #150 million for Northern Ireland.
OL,11,F"Those aren't resources that we have
OL,12,Fat our disposal so we will continue to
OL,13,Fengage with the government to see
OL,14,Fwhich of these changes will apply in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland and continue to make
OL,16,Fthe case to make sure that those in
OL,17,Fneed are protected at the same time as
OL,18,Fprotecting tax payers as well."
