OL,6,FHe added: "First of all we need to
OL,7,Fwork out exactly what the implications
OL,8,Fare for Northern Ireland, but I will
OL,9,Fbe very upfront and recognise the
OL,10,Fpotential cost of these changes is
OL,11,Fsignificant and those aren't resources
OL,12,Fthat we have.
