OL,3,CStormont to 'work out implications for
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland' of benefits shake-up
OL,6,F"What I will be wanting to do is
OL,7,Fengage with the government, take part
OL,8,Fin that process of consultation as
OL,9,Fwell, and my objective is to make sure
OL,10,Fthat we put the best argument forward
OL,11,Fto the government because we simply
OL,12,Fdon't have the resources here in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland to mitigate against
OL,14,Fthose changes."
OL,16,FEarlier, speaking in the Assembly, Ms
OL,17,FO'Neill said she plans to raise the
OL,18,Fchanges with the Government.
