OL,3,CStormont to 'work out implications for
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland' of benefits shake-up
OL,6,F"I think that this is yet again more
OL,7,Fof the same from this Government in
OL,8,FLondon," she said, referencing the
OL,9,Fprevious cut to winter fuel payments
OL,10,Fand an increase to employers' national
OL,11,Finsurance contributions.
OL,13,F"Now they're reaching for people with
OL,14,Fdisabilities, and those that are sick
OL,15,Fand vulnerable in our society," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
