OL,3,CStormont to 'work out implications for
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland' of benefits shake-up
OL,6,F"These are political choices,
OL,7,Fpolitical choices being made in London
OL,8,Fthat are impacting detrimentally on
OL,9,Four lives here, and we don't have a
OL,10,Fsay in that.
OL,12,F"So I think that targeting the most
OL,13,Fvulnerable in our society through
OL,14,Fthese punitive taxes is clearly a
OL,15,Fpolitical choice in London, but it
OL,16,Fdoes not serve the interests of our
OL,17,Fpeople here.
